                     <interp inst="t17920215-34-off192" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17920215-34-cd193" type="crimeDate">7th day of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920215-34-off192 t17920215-34-cd193"></join>, one piece of silk handkerchief, containing fourteen handkerchiefs, value 64 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17920215-34-victim438" type="victimName">
                           Alexander 
                           Blythe
                        <interp inst="t17920215-34-victim438" type="surname" value="Blythe"></interp>
