                     <interp inst="t17920215-34-person446" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a constable, and took the prisoner, and marked the goods.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I was going on an errand into Holborn for my master.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner called three witnesses, who gave him a good character.)</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17920215-34-verdict194" type="verdictDescription">
